### 5.3 Data Typography

```css
/* Hero stats with metallic gradient */
.stat-value-hero {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 800;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85) 100%);
